rows.label: tlk41200122_02_msg0001
rows.name:
It's gunna be okay, Armoo...
You're safe now...

rows.label: tlk41200122_02_msg0002
rows.name:
No, we are not okay! All the Armoo got
super scared when that water tower
fell over!

rows.label: tlk41200122_02_msg0003
rows.name:
An' the grazing land's all gone squishy
and mushy...

rows.label: tlk41200122_02_msg0004
rows.name:
It's all Iira's fault! If they're gonna
call for backup, they should do it
more quiet-like!

rows.label: tlk41200122_02_msg0005
rows.name:
There, there, little Armoo.
It's gonna be okay...
